d it's mother into uselessness, we decided to break the trend. <br><br>See Hidden Changes: <br><br>- Is now free to all assassins with at least 5 points in stealth. <br>- We have changed the properties of See Hidden to allow you to see through walls, keeps, trees, etc. <br>- See Hidden has had its name changed to X-RAY Vision. <br>- Now you can see through the players Epic armor, giving you a +50% damage due to finding their soft spots easier. <br>- With the name change to X-RAY vision, we have also decided that to have such a totally sweet ability like that, you need other things to balance it out, Temporary invulnerability, Glacier Giant strength, and the ability to climb air (fly) have also been added. <br><br>True Sight Changes: <br><br>- Archers who trained in Bow to 50th get True sight for free. <br>- You have to have a 253 Dex to use this ability, any more or less and it will not function properly. <br>- To activate it you must take at least 10 points of damage, Falling damage doesn’t count since it is self-inflicted. <br>- While using True Sight, your character will be unable to move, due to concentrating on invisible targets. <br>- If you try to move your character immediately loses true sight and takes 50% of your current hp in Damage. <br>- The cost of True sight has been changed to 19 RA points, to put it in line with Ignore Pain. <br>- If an Assassin class comes into view, your character immediately begins /yelling so as to allow other people to find you, and help you kill the assassin. <br>- The Name of True Sight has been changed to SUPER X-RAY Vision, to be more powerful of a sounding name than the Assassin ability. <br><br><br>=================================== <br><br>Compliments of Tyfund <br><br>===================================== <br>-----signature----- <br><br>Taco <br>Morte Noire- Never will your legacy be forgotten <br>Ranger and Dem Proud of it!!!! <br>Team Leader Rangers <br>Bane of Yggdra Forrest  <p></